WEBVTT

00:00:00.719 --> 00:00:03.429
Well, good evening, family. Thank you for

00:00:03.439 --> 00:00:06.309
joining us again today. We're going

00:00:06.319 --> 00:00:08.549
to pray tonight. I want to pray more

00:00:08.559 --> 00:00:10.549
than talk.

00:00:10.559 --> 00:00:13.430
And so, I want to go over

00:00:13.440 --> 00:00:15.509
some of the things we have in the

00:00:15.519 --> 00:00:18.870
news since I've been with you last.

00:00:18.880 --> 00:00:22.070
There's a lot going on, as everybody can

00:00:22.080 --> 00:00:26.630
see. Paris is on fire.

00:00:26.640 --> 00:00:30.870
If you all remember,

00:00:30.880 --> 00:00:34.549
I saw the Eiffel Tower on fire and I

00:00:34.559 --> 00:00:36.310
said, 'It's burning.'And I don't know

00:00:36.320 --> 00:00:38.470
