00:01:36.320 --> 00:01:37.429
And then,

00:01:37.439 --> 00:01:39.510
so they're burning tires or something.

00:01:39.520 --> 00:01:41.590
Yeah.

00:01:41.600 --> 00:01:43.910
And that's what I saw in the spirit. And

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:46.389
so they're popping fireworks, and they're

00:01:46.399 --> 00:01:48.950
rioting, and doing... I said,

00:01:48.960 --> 00:01:51.350
