00:02:01.200 --> 00:02:04.789
Two years ago,

00:02:04.799 --> 00:02:06.230
they're burning everything up just like

00:02:06.240 --> 00:02:09.510
I saw there. I saw things in

00:02:09.520 --> 00:02:13.030
